title: Rent-A-Girlfriend
description:
Rent-A-Girlfriend simulpub chapters available for those out of region to access K MANGA chapters of the series. This is a collection of chapters since K Manga started simultaneously publishing the series in English, starting from chapter 281 since May 2023 to ongoing current chapters.

281-ongoing from K MANGA
280-previous scan groups: KanoKari When?!, Black Cat Scans, Kanojo Okarishimasu Scans
 
Chapters 280 and previous are from the scan groups that helped the series reach international readers before official translations started simulpub. Official English volumes only started its release in June 2020. All chapters titles use the official English translation.
author: Reiji Miyajima
